# Design Toolkit Guide -- Building UI Without MCP Plugins

> This guide teaches AI agents and developers how to build pixel-accurate UI
> by reading specs and applying the design system tokens. No Figma MCP or
> design plugins required.

---

## Spec Reading Process

When you receive a UI task, follow this sequence:

1. **Read the task file** -- it contains the screen name and acceptance criteria
2. **Read the service hub** -- it lists all screens and their routes
3. **Read the design system** (`foundations/design-system.md`) -- tokens and patterns
4. **Read the spec** (if linked in `{{SPEC_LAYER_PATH}}`) -- wireframes and field lists
5. **Check existing components** (`components/_index.md`) -- reuse before building

