## Component Selection Guide

| Need | Reach For | Why |
|------|-----------|-----|
| Data table with sort/filter | `{{TABLE_COMPONENT}}` | Pre-built pagination, sorting |
| Form with validation | `{{FORM_COMPONENT}}` + field components | Consistent validation UX |
| Status indicator | `StatusBadge` / `DotLabel` | Maps to status color system |
| Page layout | `{{LAYOUT_COMPONENT}}` | Sidebar + header + content |
| Modal / dialog | `{{DIALOG_COMPONENT}}` | Accessible, focus-trapped |
| Dropdown menu | `{{DROPDOWN_COMPONENT}}` | Keyboard navigable |
| Toast / notification | `{{TOAST_COMPONENT}}` | Auto-dismiss, stacking |

