## Color Reference (Quick Lookup)

### Primary Actions
- **Primary button/link:** `bg-primary text-primary-foreground`
- **Secondary button:** `bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground`
- **Destructive:** `bg-destructive text-white`
- **Ghost:** `bg-transparent hover:bg-accent`

### Surfaces
- **Page background:** `bg-background`
- **Card:** `bg-card border border-border rounded-{{BRAND_RADIUS}}`
- **Muted area:** `bg-muted text-muted-foreground`

### Text
- **Primary text:** `text-foreground`
- **Secondary text:** `text-muted-foreground`
- **Link text:** `text-primary hover:underline`

