## Status Badge Patterns

Use the 8-family status color system for all status indicators.

```tsx
// Dot-label badge pattern
<span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium
  bg-status-{family}-bg text-status-{family}-text border border-status-{family}-border">
  <span className="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-status-{family}-dot" />
  {label}
</span>
```

| Status Text | Family | Example Use |
|-------------|--------|-------------|
| Active, Delivered, Paid | `success` | Load delivered, invoice paid |
| Pending, Under Review | `warning` | Awaiting approval |
| Failed, Rejected, Overdue | `danger` | Payment failed, load cancelled |
| New, Open | `info` | New load, open ticket |
| Draft, Inactive | `neutral` | Unpublished, archived |
| In Transit, Processing | `in-progress` | Load moving, payment processing |
| Scheduled, Queued | `queued` | Future dispatch, queued job |
| Priority, Featured | `special` | VIP customer, hot load |

