## Form Patterns

### Standard Form Layout
```tsx
<form className="space-y-6">
  {/* Section with heading */}
  <div className="space-y-4">
    <h3 className="text-lg font-medium">Section Title</h3>
    {/* Two-column grid for related fields */}
    <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <FormField />
      <FormField />
    </div>
  </div>
  {/* Action bar */}
  <div className="flex justify-end gap-3 pt-4 border-t">
    <Button variant="outline">Cancel</Button>
    <Button type="submit">Save</Button>
  </div>
</form>
```

### Field Sizing Guide
| Field Type | Width | Notes |
|-----------|-------|-------|
| Short text (name, code) | `md:col-span-1` | Half width on desktop |
| Long text (description) | `md:col-span-2` | Full width |
| Select / dropdown | `md:col-span-1` | Half width |
| Date picker | `md:col-span-1` | Half width |
| Textarea | `md:col-span-2` | Full width, min 3 rows |
| Phone / email | `md:col-span-1` | Half width |

